HEADWORD: Painim
<hw>Pai"nim</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>painime</ets> pagans, paganism, fr. OF. <ets>paienisme</ets>
paganism, LL. <ets>paganismus</ets>. See <er>Paganism</er>,
<er>Pagan</er>.]</ety> <def>A pagan; an infidel; -- used also
adjectively.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>panim</asp> and
<asp>paynim</asp>.]</altsp> <rj><au>Peacham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

